Had to piece together the little videos and Live Photos I had. These were all the photos/video I was able to get from my sister’s shower! It’s totally different when it is your own event, there is no time for anything 🙈
Thank you @juanrraorozco for the beautiful florals and @sweetmagiccreations for the beautiful and delicious cake!

Big thanks to all the team that made this event such a success, and a special thanks to Veronica’s Specialties for entrusting Orozco’s Floral Designs on this personal event! Looking forward to new designs in future with you!

Veronica’s Specialties x Vanessa’s Decorations 
This collaboration was the wedding of Veronica’s youngest daughter/ my sister, Renata. The Bride had a vision and @vanessas_decorations and her team worked hard around the clock to make that vision a reality. Thank you so much for all of your hard work, we could not have done it without you. 

To @juanrraorozco for all of his hard work as well, thank you for all of the beautiful florals 🙏 we appreciate you so much!! 

A special thank you to: 

 @dancefloordesigns for the dance floor vinyls  and signs

 @exclusivedjgroup for helping us create the false ceiling for the dance floor and also being our dj for the night!
